### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/index.php?route=health

### Search flights
GET http://localhost:8000/index.php?route=flights/search&origin=Montreal&destination=Paris&date=2026-05-18

### List reservations
GET http://localhost:8000/index.php?route=reservations

### Create reservation
POST http://localhost:8000/index.php?route=reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schedule_id": 1,
  "first_name": "Carolina",
  "last_name": "Konan",
  "email": "carolina@example.com",
  "phone": "+1-514-444-1234",
  "passport_number": "CA999888",
  "nationality": "Canadian",
  "seat_number": "14B"
}

### Track itinerary
GET http://localhost:8000/index.php?route=itineraries/reservation/1
